<TITLE> Algorithms for Analysing the Temporal Structure of Discourse </TITLE>
<AUTHORS>
<AUTHOR>Janet Hitzeman</AUTHOR>
<AUTHOR>Marc Moens</AUTHOR>
<AUTHOR>Claire Grover</AUTHOR>
